<bibRefCitation author="Johnson" bookContentInfo="205 figs." box="[980,1143,907,933]" firstAuthor="Johnson" journalOrPublisher="Reports of the Museum of Natural History, University of Wisconsin, Stevens Point" pageId="11" pageNumber="22" pagination="1 - 135" part="2" refId="ref22864" refString="Johnson, K. (1992) Genera and species of the Neotropical &quot; elfin &quot; - like hairstreak butterflies (Lepidoptera, Lycaenidae, Theclinae). Reports of the Museum of Natural History, University of Wisconsin, Stevens Point, 22 (1 &amp; 2), 1 - 135, 205 figs. &amp; 136 - 279 + 241, 2 figs." title="Genera and species of the Neotropical &quot; elfin &quot; - like hairstreak butterflies (Lepidoptera, Lycaenidae, Theclinae)" type="book chapter" year="1992">Johnson, 1992</bibRefCitation>
