<bibRefCitation author="d'Abrera" box="[1187,1424,1014,1041]" firstAuthor="d'Abrera" journalOrPublisher="Hill House, Black Rock, Victoria" page="1137" pageId="11" pageNumber="22" pagination="1098 - 1270" refId="ref22067" refString="D'Abrera, B. (1995) In: Butterflies of the Neotropical Region. Part VII. Lycaenidae. Hill House, Black Rock, Victoria, pp. i - xi + 1098 - 1270." type="book chapter" volumeTitle="Butterflies of the Neotropical Region. Part VII. Lycaenidae" year="1995">d’Abrera 1995: 1137</bibRefCitation>
